data.description: Enjoy the gorgeous hill country sunset from this incredible custom home, perfectly positioned in The Bluffs of Rough Hollow. Built by Seven Custom Homes, this 5 bedroom, 5 bath home is filled with luxury details and thoughtful design elements. Relax on the large covered back patio, overlooking the sparkling, oversized lap pool with a vast hill country view. The elegant front door and huge back sliding doors allow natural light to flow through the open floor plan. The living room boasts 2 story ceilings, a custom fireplace, built-ins, and is open to the gourmet kitchen. The Primary Bedroom and impressive Primary Bathroom are on the first floor, along with a guest bedroom and additional full bath. Upstairs, you will find 3 spacious bedrooms (each with a private bathroom) and a huge game room with a covered patio. Views of Lake Travis from the upstairs patio and secondary bedroom. 3 car garage with Tesla charging station. Take advantage of the impressive community amenities: Rough Hollow Yacht Club & Marina, luxury swimming pools, community fitness center, parks, nature trails, and Canyon Grille. Desirable Lake Travis ISD, with Serene Hills Elementary in walking distance. This home truly offers the best of Lake Travis living!
